        ],
        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "You started in kitchens as a teenager, doing dishes and collecting things from the pantry. Over the years you worked your way up to being a senior sous chef, and decided to open your own restaurant. That exploded into a series of restaurants and you moved from being a chef to a manager of a network of such restaurants, popular places for both middle class and wealthy people to go and eat. You had an eye for location, opportunity and talent to work the kitchens. This drew the attention of your sire, who saw in you a talent for management and who needed someone to help run their own vast network of ghouls. You did so well at it, you began building your own network of influence.\n\nYou've been in Las Vegas for the last couple of years, working on your own business interests there. But you woke up one evening to one of your chefs, a ghoul who you trusted with your most elite restaurant, warning you to make a run for it. You didn't need telling twice. You don't know what happened, but you made it out to Los Angeles, where you also had influences, at least to lay low for a while and see what is going on. Prince Petrovna has been understanding of you coming in and out, but you may have to make this your permanent place of residence for a while until you figure out what is going on and decide how to move your influences around to best protect your interests."
        ],
